title: Fly into Kern Country and land on the updated Inyokern Airport #msfs2020
description:
Inyokern Airport (IATA: IYK, ICAO: KIYK, FAA LID: IYK) is a public use airport located 1 nautical mile (1.9 km; 1.2 mi) northwest of the central business district of Inyokern, in Kern County, California, United States. It is owned by the Indian Wells Valley Airport District and serves the Indian Wells Valley area. The airport is mostly used for general aviation and was previously served by a number of commuter and regional airlines over the years with passenger flights to Los Angeles (LAX). This addon will add some nice details which makes flying really more realistic. So if you love flying into Kern County this is an airport which you might want to add to you shopping list.
